{"tid":2347188,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"日書籍暢銷排行遭鬼滅之刃「屠榜」榜單看不見其他作品","createTime":"2020-12-31T00:30:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T20:40:13.000Z","uid":25345,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3cc3ee46f6a5587d0f149a3881eed1478de9f6d2","tid":2347188,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T00:30:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/12/30/1/10323552.png&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=800&amp;exp=3600&amp;w=930&amp;nt=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F12%2F30%2F1%2F10323552.png%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D800%26exp%3D3600%26w%3D930%26nt%3D1&h=de2f37af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本漫畫《鬼滅之刃》今年席捲全球，劇場版在日前突破317億日圓（約新台幣85億9836萬），打破《神隱少女》的316億日圓紀錄，正式登上日本影史票房冠軍。除了電影賣座，原作漫畫也「屠榜」，佔據第1～22名，放眼望去榜單上只見鬼滅的書名。<br />\n<br />\n根據日本Oricon發表的2020暢銷書籍排行榜，《鬼滅之刃》在漫畫榜達成「完全制霸」的成就，發售的22集漫畫佔據前1～22名，其中冠軍的18集單行本就賣破439萬。由於該排行榜只統計到11月底，最終的23集是12月才發售，所以未列入榜單。<br />\n<br />\n今年五月Oricon也公布過一次2020上半年漫畫銷量排行，《鬼滅之刃》就已達到佔據第1至19名的創舉，今回更是再次打破紀錄，列入統計的22集全上榜，總銷量突破9000萬。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/12/30/1/10323601.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=800&amp;exp=3600&amp;w=800&amp;nt=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F12%2F30%2F1%2F10323601.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D800%26exp%3D3600%26w%3D800%26nt%3D1&h=27b84f38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不只強佔漫畫榜，在2020綜合書籍的排行榜中，《鬼滅之刃》的兩部短篇小說分別以92萬和91萬登上冠亞軍，7月出版的第三集小說則以60萬排到第五名。幫鬼滅撰寫小說的作者矢島綾這三部小說總計賣出264多萬，奪得2020作家榜第一名。<br />\n<br />\n除了鬼滅之刃以外的作品，日本長青漫畫《航海王》的95～97集單行本排上第23～25名，總計銷量約為570多萬。然而第23名的航海王95集賣出200多萬，和第22名的鬼滅之刃21集仍有60多萬的差距。"},{"pid":"0f42c852cc8de1d4e76ec40fce378007f646664b","tid":2347188,"uid":331590,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T00:38:45.000Z","msg":"嘩~~鬼滅呀~神作呀~好勁呀~嘩~~~<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbfc455c4ab1ded41580180cdfafc79f6c5e8d30","tid":2347188,"uid":43785,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T00:41:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A6JC4Jp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA6JC4Jp.jpg&h=3d9e8a99&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b16ef32cbc90fe97f4eda4bc865c77a2a65cd265","tid":2347188,"uid":25345,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T00:44:26.000Z","msg":"垃圾海賊王仲有200萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c16e110f59991f8411ba576b1285a33904612d33","tid":2347188,"uid":165339,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dbfc455c4ab1ded41580180cdfafc79f6c5e8d30","tid":2347188,"uid":43785,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T00:41:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A6JC4Jp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA6JC4Jp.jpg&h=3d9e8a99&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T01:02:10.000Z","msg":"不死川唔係冇死咩？"},{"pid":"905a8e1b9454bbd74b0a93f76caca4da5e3e17bf","tid":2347188,"uid":128923,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c16e110f59991f8411ba576b1285a33904612d33","tid":2347188,"uid":165339,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dbfc455c4ab1ded41580180cdfafc79f6c5e8d30","tid":2347188,"uid":43785,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T00:41:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A6JC4Jp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA6JC4Jp.jpg&h=3d9e8a99&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T01:02:10.000Z","msg":"不死川唔係冇死咩？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T03:02:45.000Z","msg":"唯一無損無爛比鳩蛇話死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/n